  "prompt": "What are some alternatives to yelp in India?",
  "response": "Here are some alternatives to Yelp in India:\n\n1. Zomato\n- Popular restaurant and food review platform\n- Covers multiple cities across India\n- Provides ratings, reviews, menus, and delivery options\n\n2. Justdial\n- Local business directory and review platform\n- Covers various services including restaurants, hotels, and professional services\n- Available across multiple cities in India\n\n3. Google Maps\n- Provides user reviews and ratings for restaurants and businesses\n- Widely used and easily accessible\n- Offers location information and contact details\n\n4. Dineout\n- Restaurant discovery and booking platform\n- Offers discounts and deals\n- Provides reviews and ratings\n\n5. EazyDiner\n- Restaurant reservation and review platform\n- Offers curated restaurant recommendations\n- Provides user reviews and ratings\n\n6. Magicpin\n- Local business discovery platform\n- Offers cashback and rewards\n- Covers restaurants, shopping, and services\n\n7. TripAdvisor\n- International platform with extensive restaurant and hotel reviews\n- Provides user-generated content\n- Covers multiple cities in India\n\n8. RestroApp\n- Restaurant discovery and review platform\n- Focuses on local restaurants\n- Provides user ratings and reviews\n\nThese platforms offer similar functionalities to Yelp and can help users find and review local businesses in India.",
